00:01:20.949 --> 00:01:24.819 position:21% line:83% align:start
At least it happened
at the end of the trip.

00:01:24.953 --> 00:01:28.556 position:30% line:83% align:start
That was a lot,
and I kinda panicked.

00:01:28.690 --> 00:01:32.359 position:21% line:83% align:start
It was super special.
You were my first.

00:01:32.492 --> 00:01:35.162 position:27% line:83% align:start
So, uh, was that
the same for you?

00:01:35.295 --> 00:01:39.232 position:41% line:83% align:start
[JIRO]
Uh! Well, I mean...

00:01:40.702 --> 00:01:44.104 position:16% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Our kiss in the
nurse's office wasn't his first.

00:01:44.237 --> 00:01:46.608 position:30% line:89% align:start
So that's that.

00:01:46.741 --> 00:01:51.746 position:19% line:83% align:start
I tried not to see it,
but now it's so obvious.

00:01:55.650 --> 00:01:59.219 position:19% line:83% align:start
Jiro's wife always has
been and will be Akari.

00:01:59.353 --> 00:02:01.288 position:19% line:83% align:start
Does that mean I'm just
his childhood friend

00:02:01.421 --> 00:02:02.724 position:27% line:89% align:start
