00:02:02.857 --> 00:02:07.160 position:33% line:83% align:start
If so, yucky!
I'm basically a homewrecker.

00:02:13.067 --> 00:02:19.007 position:19% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Jiro? What did
that kiss mean to you?

00:02:19.139 --> 00:02:23.778 position:16% line:89% align:start
Cause for me... Oh, Jiro.

00:03:56.704 --> 00:04:00.508 position:27% line:83% align:start
[JIRO] Aw, crap.
What am I supposed to do?

00:04:03.611 --> 00:04:05.980 position:41% line:83% align:start
[JIRO]
Huh? The hell?

00:04:06.114 --> 00:04:07.849 position:44% line:89% align:start
Why?

00:04:10.283 --> 00:04:12.587 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI]
I am so sorry.

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:14.756 position:30% line:83% align:start
