being your childhood friend

00:04:14.889 --> 00:04:17.992 position:24% line:83% align:start
won't be enough to
keep me in your life.

00:04:25.398 --> 00:04:29.237 position:7% line:83% align:start
[JIRO] Aren't games supposed to
be an escape from real life?

00:04:29.369 --> 00:04:31.706 position:21% line:83% align:start
