like that was my one shot.

00:04:37.712 --> 00:04:39.446 position:24% line:83% align:start
Like if that moment
had been perfect,

00:04:39.580 --> 00:04:44.218 position:16% line:83% align:start
this love I've held onto
might become something real.

00:04:44.384 --> 00:04:46.187 position:27% line:83% align:start
I guess it wasn't
perfect though.

00:04:46.319 --> 00:04:47.889 position:7% line:89% align:start
Beside a barrage of apologies,

00:04:48.022 --> 00:04:50.625 position:27% line:83% align:start
"let's head back"
was all she had to say.

00:04:50.758 --> 00:04:54.662 position:10% line:83% align:start
What did it mean to her, and
why kiss me just to apologize

00:04:54.796 --> 00:04:58.266 position:13% line:83% align:start
for it? You're supposed to
go on dates and fall in love

00:04:58.398 --> 00:05:00.300 position:30% line:83% align:start
and confess and
hold hands and then

00:05:00.433 --> 00:05:04.672 position:19% line:83% align:start
kiss when you're ready.
Why did we jump straight to it?

00:05:04.806 --> 00:05:06.741 position:16% line:83% align:start
