about when she said

00:05:06.874 --> 00:05:09.544 position:19% line:83% align:start
being childhood friends
wouldn't be enough?

00:05:09.677 --> 00:05:12.046 position:24% line:83% align:start
What am I supposed
to do after all that?

00:05:12.180 --> 00:05:14.515 position:21% line:83% align:start
If I had more points
in the lady skill tree,

00:05:14.649 --> 00:05:17.384 position:10% line:89% align:start
I could probably answer that.

00:05:17.518 --> 00:05:19.352 position:13% line:89% align:start
But, big shocker, I don't.

00:05:19.486 --> 00:05:21.255 position:21% line:83% align:start
Guess I'll just have
to bury my sorrows

00:05:21.388 --> 00:05:23.591 position:19% line:89% align:start
in junk food and manga.

00:05:32.133 --> 00:05:35.536 position:41% line:83% align:start
[JIRO]
I didn't realize this was out.

00:05:35.670 --> 00:05:36.737 position:27% line:89% align:start
Excuse me, ma'am!

00:05:36.871 --> 00:05:38.272 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oops, sorry!

00:05:38.405 --> 00:05:41.341 position:35% line:89% align:start
