00:06:31.424 --> 00:06:33.361 position:24% line:89% align:start
Uh? Say something?

00:06:33.493 --> 00:06:37.765 position:30% line:83% align:start
[SHIORI] Mm-mm!
Not a peep. Thank you.

00:06:37.899 --> 00:06:41.068 position:21% line:83% align:start
[JIRO] What a relief!
I'm lucky I ran into her.

00:06:41.202 --> 00:06:44.906 position:24% line:83% align:start
Now the term won't
start on an awkward foot.

00:06:45.039 --> 00:06:46.774 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, this sucks.

00:06:46.908 --> 00:06:49.510 position:7% line:83% align:start
