[JIRO] I tend to run from the
romance stuff because I just

00:12:22.276 --> 00:12:25.312 position:24% line:83% align:start
don't get it. Which
feeling is friendship?

00:12:25.446 --> 00:12:27.781 position:24% line:83% align:start
